Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.10,0:05:51.80,top,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{...girlfriend!}...bạn gái!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.10,0:05:51.80,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{...girlfriend!}bạn gái!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:56.68,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,Saki-chan, Minase-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.64,0:06:01.21,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{Please don't take on the responsibility \Nfor dating two people all on your own!}Đừng tự một mình gánh lấy \N trách nhiệm từ việc bắt cá hai tay nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:03.96,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{You're an equal with the two of us.}Bọn em cũng bình đẵng với Naoya mà đúng chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.40,0:06:07.13,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{Isn't that the whole point of dating?}Đó không phải là hẹn hò ư?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:15.34,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,{I thought I couldn't be allowed to be \Nhappy until I made the two of you happy,}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.34,0:06:18.52,main,,0,0,0,,{because I'm two-timing.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:11.72,main,,0,0,0,,Chỉ bởi vì chuyện bắt cá hai tay,...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:18.37,main,,0,0,0,,Anh đã nghĩ rằng phải làm hai em yên lòng trước rồi mới có thể thấy vui được.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.26,0:06:23.72,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,{I was stupid!}Anh là một thằng đại ngốc!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.72,0:06:25.34,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,{Hit me!}Làm ơn hãy đập anh đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:26.14,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{No...}Đợi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.48,0:06:29.74,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Saki-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:34.08,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{He told me what he wanted, so...}Anh ta bảo là anh ta muốn nên...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:34.99,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,That's how you took it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:40.00,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,{That's what I like about you.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.52,0:06:44.13,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,It's why you're fun to be around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.68,0:06:46.02,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Naoya...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.63,0:06:50.88,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,{And there's a lot that I want you to do.}Và còn nhiều điều anh muốn em làm nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.46,0:06:53.76,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,{I want to see you smile more!}Anh muốn được nhìn thấy nụ cười của Saki-chan nhiều hơn nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.76,0:06:55.89,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{Y-You got it!}H-Hãy để cho em!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:57.29,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,{And I want to see you angry more!}Cả khi em giận nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:06:58.39,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{How's this?}Như thế này?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:07:00.04,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,{I want your home cooking!}Anh muốn ăn đồ em nấu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:01.71,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{I'll feed you char!}Em sẽ cho anh ăn than.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:02.99,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,{I want to see your swimsuit in summer!}Trong mùa hè, anh muốn ngắm em mặc đồ bơi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.99,0:07:04.27,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{You'll see it!}Cho anh ngắm luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:07.85,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,{And someday, a three—}Và một ngày náo đó anh sẽ ____ ba.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.85,0:07:09.15,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{Not happening!}Làm tới hả!{Cứ mơ đi!}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.52,0:07:13.41,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,{And more than anything,}Và trên hết,...mình
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.79,0:07:17.19,main,,0,0,0,,{I want the three of us to \Ncontinue living together.}Anh muốn ba đứa tiếp tục sống chung.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.91,0:07:27.78,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{I know that.}Em biết rồi mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.18,0:07:29.29,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{Jeez.}Hứ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:34.84,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Saki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.84,0:07:35.85,main,Saki,0,0,0,,Hey...}Này...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:37.31,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,{Thanks.}Cảm ơn em.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.72,0:07:40.56,main,Naoya,0,0,0,,{I'm glad you two are on the same page.}Thấy hai em có chung chí hướng làm anh rất vui.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.49,0:07:46.19,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{N-Nah, but...}Không có chi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:47.62,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{Nagisa-chan is still...}Nhưng Nagisa-chan vẫn là...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:51.02,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{my r-rival!}...tình địch của em mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.01,0:07:53.70,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{Right.}Đúng vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.06,0:07:56.78,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{I'm going to put up a fight.}Mình cũng sẽ không thua đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:07:59.58,top,,0,0,0,,{Nuh... G-g-ggh...}Hứ... gừ gừ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:08:00.33,sign_11470_119_Saki_has_returne,Text,0,0,0,,{\pos(620,570)}{Saki has returned home.}Saki đã trở về.
