Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:04.83,sign_12657_156_Happiness___,Text,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(700,40)\c&H8F6B90&\b1\fs50}Staaare...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:02.97,italics,Saki,0,0,0,,Those must be nice to squeeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:09.09,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{Saki-san, dinner's ready!}Saki-san, Cơm tối xong rồi này!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:17.85,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{I worked really hard on dinner \Nto commemorate your return.}Để mừng Saki-san quay lại,\N tớ đã làm rất nhiều cho tối nay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:19.80,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{It looks delicious.}Nhìn ngon quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.80,0:08:23.56,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{You worked so hard on this dinner,}Nagisa-chan đã nấu ra thế này rồi mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:24.94,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{and Naoya is...}Naoya lại...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.24,0:08:32.23,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{He stayed up three whole nights to \Ntry to patch things up with you.}Vì muốn hòa thuận với Nagisa-san mà anh ấy đã thức trắng ba ngày liền đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.69,0:08:34.32,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{Oh, yeah...}Ừ nhỉ....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:36.98,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{Well, let's eat before it gets cold.}Thôi, ăn nhanh kẻo đồ ăn nó nguội.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:40.20,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{Time to eat!}Tới giờ ăn rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.30,0:08:44.71,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{Yum!}Ngon quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.99,0:08:46.33,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{I'm glad you like it.}Mừng vì cậu thích.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.19,0:08:53.13,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{B-But just to be clear, \Nyou and I are still rivals.}Nhưng phải nói rõ ra. \NTừ giờ, tớ và Nagisa-chan là tình địch đấy nhé
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:55.92,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{I-I know.}T-Tớ biết mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.92,0:08:59.60,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{But I like you, Saki-san.}Nhưng mà, Tớ vẫn mến cậu Saki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:02.06,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{I want us to be friends.}Tớ muốn thân với cậu hơn nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:07.53,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{I do, too!}Tớ cũng vậy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:10.36,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{You're so adorable.}Sao mà dễ thương quá vậy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:15.07,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{Although we're playing right into \NNaoya's hands if we get friendly.}Chúng ta sẽ thân nhiều bao nhiêu \N nếu không đổ cùng một người là Naoya kia chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.52,0:09:20.83,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{You're so awesome, though!}Đúng là cậu tuyệt thật!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.32,0:09:23.87,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{It'll be so much fun if we become friends!}Nếu biết cậu sớm hơn thì sẽ vui hơn nhiều.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:25.58,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{Y-You have high expectations.}Cậu đề cao quá đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:28.35,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{No matter what we do, it'll be fun as hell!}Dù có làm gì với nhau đi nữa cũng sẽ vui hết biết!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.35,0:09:28.96,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{Wait...}Đợi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.44,0:09:34.54,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{So how are we going to be friends?}Tiện thể, làm sao để chúng ta \Nthành bạn tốt của nhau đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.44,0:09:38.97,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{I happen to like gaming.}Tớ rất thích chơi game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.65,0:09:41.10,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:46.10,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{Will you play with me?!}Muốn chơi game chung với nhau không?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:51.11,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{I used to play that game.}Mình từng chơi qua game đó rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:52.75,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{I'd totally do that.}Nếu là như thế thì ổn thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.75,0:09:54.11,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{Really?!}Không thể nào?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.88,0:09:59.79,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{So how many hours did you play?}Tiện đây, Nagisa-chan có bao nhiêu\N tiếng trong game rồi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.79,0:10:00.72,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{Um...}Ừ thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:02.37,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{Probably about 1,000 hours.}Tầm đâu đó 1000 giờ.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:04.67,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{Seriously? Wow!}Thiệt không?! Tuyệt thật!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:06.57,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{I'm not good at it, though.}Mình không chơi tốt đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.57,0:10:09.02,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{Would you really say that \Nafter 1,000 hours?}Nghe người chơi 1000 giờ nói kìa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:10.50,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{No, I'm really not.}Không, thật đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:12.01,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{Sure, sure.}Rồi, rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.01,0:10:13.55,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{Let's see what you've got.}Để xem cậu tới đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.87,0:10:15.20,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{I can't wait!}Vào nhanh đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:17.38,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{I'll d-do what I can!}Tớ sẽ cố hết sức.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:25.26,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{Huh? You're dead already?}Hả? mới đó đã chết rồi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.26,0:10:27.18,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{S-Sorry.}Xin lỗi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.18,0:10:29.94,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{Don't worry. It's all right.}Không sao, ổn cả thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:33.48,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{Okay, could you scout from \Nthe top of the mountain?}Trận tới, nhờ cậu lên núi ngăm băng nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:34.15,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{Okay.}Để tớ thử.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:37.15,sign_15216_172_Gravity,Text,0,0,0,,{\blur8\frz15\move(760,360,760,370)\t(1,2540,\frz21.5)\fad(941,1)\fscx70}{FALL}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:39.75,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{Sorry.}Thật sự xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.38,0:10:43.59,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{You can at least drive, right?}Ít nhất thì cậu vẫn lái được xe đúng không?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.09,0:10:46.66,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{I'm going to crash!}Sắp tông rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:49.92,sign_15216_172_Gravity,Text,0,0,0,,{\move(790,130,752,140)\frz-33.54\t(1,2840,\frz-21.06)\fad(941,1)}{CRASH}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:51.85,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{You really do suck.}Tệ thật luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.85,0:10:54.54,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{Can anyone who's played \N1,000 hours be this bad?}Có ai chơi 1000 giờ mà tệ thế này ư?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.86,0:10:57.42,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry I couldn't live \Nup to your expectations.}Xin lỗi đã làm cậu thất vọng.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:11:01.99,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{It's not fun playing with me, is it?}chơi game với tớ có vẻ không được vui lắm nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:04.22,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{That's not true.}Không phải thế đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.31,0:11:07.68,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{Carrying the team is actually fun!}Thực ra tớ rất thích gánh team.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.26,0:11:10.99,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{I can really show off my skills!}có như thế mới thể hiện được thực lực của mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.99,0:11:12.69,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{Really?}Thật ư?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:14.40,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{All right.}Vậy thì.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:18.14,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{We aren't going to sleep \Nuntil I get you a kill.}Chúng ta sẽ không ngủ cho đến khi\N Nagisa-chan có được một mạng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:20.78,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{I don't think we'll ever get to sleep, then.}Như vậy có khi sẽ không ngủ được mất.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:22.04,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{Don't worry.}Khỏi lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:24.82,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{Just follow me.}Bám theo tớ thôi là được.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.82,0:11:26.18,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{O-Okay.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:28.28,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{Enemy footsteps!}Có tiếng chân.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:30.25,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{Ahead!}Phía trước kìa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.84,0:11:33.68,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{They got me again.}Lại bị bắt nữa rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.68,0:11:34.71,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{Oh, dear.}Ôi ôi ôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.11,0:11:36.46,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{It's all right.}Được thôi, được thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:39.40,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{I'll help you... out!}Tớ sẽ ra cứu cậu... liền!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:45.98,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{You're so good, Saki-san!}Saki-san giởi quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.98,0:11:47.26,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{Nah.}Có gì đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:50.19,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{You're so cute when you die right away, too.}Nagisa-chan để chết liền luôn cũng đáng yêu nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.19,0:11:51.64,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{How is that cute?}Sao mà đáng yêu được?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:53.40,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{Come on.}Nhanh lên, nhanh lên.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.99,0:11:56.18,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{Hurry over here!}Nhanh đến đây không thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.92,0:11:59.02,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{Not again.}Lại nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.02,0:12:01.15,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{Okay, one more time}Xong rồi, thêm ván nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.28,0:12:09.85,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{I'll give poor widdle you all my heals.}Tớ cho cậu hết băng quấn nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:11.66,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{Am I a baby now?!}Tớ thành em bé rồi sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:19.80,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{It looks like you're having \Na lot more fun now.}Có vẽ như cậu vui lên hẵng rồi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.27,0:12:22.14,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{Yeah!}Đúng vậy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.14,0:12:26.05,main,Saki,0,0,0,,{I'm having fun besting you\N at something for the first time!}Dụ Nagisa-chan chết trước nãy giờ rất vui.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.38,0:12:28.05,main,Nagisa,0,0,0,,{I'm having mixed feelings!}Cảm thấy rối bời.
